msgid "Stopping Effektif"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/stopping.rst:3
msgid ""
"In order to stop the Effektif system completely, you have to stop the Tomcat"
" application server and the MongoDB database. However, if you need to "
"restart the Effektif system, it is sufficient to restart only the Tomcat "
"server."
msgstr ""

